{"tid":2447093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國產電視開機焗睇廣告  苦主斥欺騙 擬控告小米","createTime":"2021-03-15T03:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T04:22:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"68d2397db7ff19a5fa0ee575f869d91b7788888f","tid":2447093,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:10:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210315/53J4KDGEFZF45IZ7NDGGUSSUKM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210315%2F53J4KDGEFZF45IZ7NDGGUSSUKM%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDpuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=423790fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210315%2F53J4KDGEFZF45IZ7NDGGUSSUKM%2F&h=cc6a1a31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210315/53J4KDGEFZF45IZ7NDGGUSSUKM/</a><br />\n<br />\n國產電視開機焗睇廣告 <br />\n苦主斥欺騙 擬控告小米<br />\n<br />\n內地智能電視普遍有開機時強制播放廣告的狀況，今日是國際消費者權益日，內媒發佈調查報道，指多個品牌的智能電視，開機時會自動播放15至30秒的廣告，大部份都不能關閉，有的聲稱能關閉的，也到最後5秒才可以，其中包括小米、夏普等品牌。有購買了小米電視，但被開機廣告困擾的苦主稱擬起訴小米，指自己購買時沒獲告知開機廣告的事，安裝後才發現，「這不是欺騙消費者嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港人貪平買水貨中伏：煩到癲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PUuL5KVpAKE5UPBkQOz9VHY4en4=/2624x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TNUSI2TU6REODIBM332X4ADD2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPUuL5KVpAKE5UPBkQOz9VHY4en4%3D%2F2624x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTNUSI2TU6REODIBM332X4ADD2Y.jpg&h=3f07f30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有港人購買內地品牌智能電視前不知附設開機廣告。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n澎湃新聞網昨報道，現在市面上常見的12個品牌的智能電視中。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wkdVdiQYOO7FRFvyd9qMcIXSEmM=/2000x460/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DOUMFBSUF5F5XIU342XF2IFLCI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwkdVdiQYOO7FRFvyd9qMcIXSEmM%3D%2F2000x460%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDOUMFBSUF5F5XIU342XF2IFLCI.gif&h=2d144798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手機用戶請按此放大圖表<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n顧客要求退貨遭拒<br />\n<br />\n廣州市民梁凱（化名）指自己農曆新年前以2,899元（約3,460港元）購買了一台65吋的小米全面屏電視，發現每次開電視都要先看30秒廣告，「只有看到最後5秒才能跳過，但都已經被迫觀看25秒了」。他認為購買時小米沒有告知自己會有開機廣告，存欺騙之嫌，要求退貨遭拒，便向廣州市消費者委員會投訴，更稱若問題無法改善，將會起訴小米公司。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，這也非小米首次因為。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有四川民眾2018年以約8,000元（約9,540港元）購買一部夏普智能電視，去年年底電視系統自動更新後，出現以往沒有的商業廣告，他多次要求取消開機廣告或者設置成一鍵跳過，均被告知無法做到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n硬件盈利少 靠廣告補貼<br />\n<br />\n江蘇消保委前年曾對電視開機廣告進行專案行動，當時除樂視外，多家廠商均承諾進行整改，當局隨即對樂視電視提起訴訟，判決結果去年11月出爐，指樂視開機廣告侵犯消費者選擇。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n內地開機廣告的確有價有市，據知每千次流量價格為45至50元（47.8至59.6港元。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n澎湃新聞網/《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"7dd324260c1862ebcb94aadeaaf4cb974c19b47d","tid":2447093,"uid":3553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:19:00.000Z","msg":"難怪咁撚平<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港啲大陸牌子都係？"},{"pid":"1910ea82d8ef4fc5d34d7a5b9202ede8e9be6d77","tid":2447093,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:20:25.000Z","msg":"唔告正契弟"},{"pid":"3a8996aaf84ec7587638eeb5708bf2d16dc00cff","tid":2447093,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:42:49.000Z","msg":"唔播開機廣告<br />\n改播關機廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拆電再開機果陣會重播<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee99c39dd59c9c75f03967adcd43252abd5613d0","tid":2447093,"uid":33096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:46:36.000Z","msg":"自己on9姐買大陸電視炸死都無得賠，更何況依家淨係比廣告你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw唔告正契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616a3869bc56a375740460b63108